            "first_air_time": "2010-07-27",
            "overview": "Ra's al Ghul realizes his mistake in hiring Joker (character) to use him as a distraction while Ra's destroyed Europe's financial districts. In Sarajevo, Bosnia, the Joker brutally assaults Jason Todd, the second Robin (comics), in an abandoned warehouse with a crowbar. Jason is locked in the warehouse with a bomb, which explodes and kills him before Batman arrives.",
