            "overview": "Batman returns home to Gotham City after 12 years abroad, training for his eventual one-man war on crime; Lieutenant James Gordon (comics) moves to Gotham with his pregnant wife, Barbara, after a transfer from Chicago. Both are swiftly acquainted with the corruption and violence of Gotham City, with Gordon witnessing his partner Arnold John Flass assaulting a teen for fun.",
