            "id": "movie-3238",
            "image_url": "https://artworks.thetvdb.com/banners/movies/3238/posters/3238.jpg",
            "name": "Superman/Batman: Public Enemies",
            "first_air_time": "2009-09-29",
            "overview": "Lex Luthor has been elected President of the United States during a severe nationwide Depression. Under his leadership, the economy begins to thrive, and he assembles a force of government-employed superheroes consisting of Captain Atom, Katana, Black Lightning, Power Girl, Starfire, and Major Force. Superman and Batman maintain their distrust toward Luthor.",
            "primary_language": "eng",
            "primary_type": "movie",
            "status": "Released",
            "type": "movie",
            "tvdb_id": "3238",
            "year": "2009",
            "slug": "supermanbatman-public-enemies",
            "overviews": {
                "eng": "Lex Luthor has been elected President of the United States during a severe nationwide Depression. Under his leadership, the economy begins to thrive, and he assembles a force of government-employed superheroes consisting of Captain Atom, Katana, Black Lightning, Power Girl, Starfire, and Major Force. Superman and Batman maintain their distrust toward Luthor.",
                "fra": "Lex Luthor est le nouveau président des États-Unis. Superman et Batman sont les deux seuls héros à s'opposer au bien-fondé d'une telle présidence. Alors qu'une météorite issue de Krypton fonce sur la Terre, un combat s'engage entre nos deux héros et les autres super-héros désormais aux ordres de Lex Luthor.",
                "spa": "Lex Luthor asume como presidente de los Estados Unidos. Con su poder, decide inculpar al hombre de acero y al murciélago en un crimen, provocando cacería por sus cabezas.",
                "tur": "Gündüz gazeteci, gece halk kahramanı Superman ve egzotik zengin Batman’in macerasında, Superman’in ölümsüz düşmanı Lex Luthor Amerika’da başkan oluyor ve dünyanın kontrolünü ele alıyor. Seçildikten sonra ilk hedefi dünyaya kryptonite yağmuru yağdırmak ve Superman tehlikesini ortadan kaldırmaktır. Fakat hesaba katmadığı bir şey vardır: Zamanı gelince Superman ve Batman güçlerini birleştirmektedir."
            },
            "translations": {
                "ces": "Superman/Batman: Veřejní nepřátelé",
