            "name": "Merry Little Batman",
            "overview": "When a six-year-old Damian Wayne finds himself alone in Wayne Manor, he must transform into \"Little Batman\" in order to defend his home and Gotham City from the crooks and super-villains intent on destroying Christmas.",
            "primary_language": "eng",
